---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import featureImg from "../../assets/template-3/feature-3.png";
---

<section class="feature-detail section">
  <div class="container flex-feature">
    <div class="feature-content">
      <span class="feature-label">Optimization for</span>
      <h2>Marketers</h2>
      <p>Few would argue that, despite the advancements of feminism over the past three decades, women still face a double standard when it comes to their behavior.</p>
      
      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="list-item">
          <h4>Accessory makers</h4>
          <p>While most people enjoy casino gambling, sports betting, lottery and bingo playing for the fun.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="list-item">
          <h4>Alterations</h4>
          <p>If you are looking for a new way to promote your business that won't cost you more money.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="list-item">
          <h4>Custom design designers</h4>
          <p>If you are looking for a new way to promote your business that won't cost you more money.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-visual">
      <Image src={featureImg} alt="Marketers" class="feature-img" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .feature-detail {
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .flex-feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 100px;
  }

  .feature-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .feature-label {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #4a4a4a;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .feature-content h2 {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .feature-content > p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #4a4a4a;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .feature-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .list-item h4 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .list-item p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #4a4a4a;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .feature-visual {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .feature-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .flex-feature { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
